data.eml:eml: Two new fossil species of Itaphlebia (Mecoptera: Nannochoristidae) from Jiulongshan Formation, Inner Mongolia, China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Liu, Nan, Zhao, Yunyun, Ren, Dong (2010): Two new fossil species of Itaphlebia (Mecoptera: Nannochoristidae) from Jiulongshan Formation, Inner Mongolia, China. Zootaxa 2420: 37-45, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.194461
